import React, { useState } from 'react';
import {
  Form,
  FormGroup,
  Label,
  Input,
  FormText,
  Button,
} from 'reactstrap';

function Formulario () {
  return (
    <Form>
      <FormGroup tag="fieldset">
        <legend>
          Radio Buttons
        </legend>
        <FormGroup check>
          <Input
            name="radio1"
            type="radio"
          />
          {' '}
          <Label check>
            Option one is this and that—be sure to include why it‘s great
          </Label>
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup check>
          <Input
            name="radio1"
            type="radio"
          />
          {' '}
          <Label check>
            Option two can be something else and selecting it will deselect option one
          </Label>
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup
          check
          disabled
        >
          <Input
            disabled
            name="radio1"
            type="radio"
          />
          {' '}
          <Label check>
            Option three is disabled
          </Label>
        </FormGroup>
      </FormGroup>
    </Form>
  );
}

export default Formulario;
